            {
                "comment": "Terrible. Exams are in a 50 minute time slot, and the questions require you to write two essays plus short answer. There is no way you can finish in that amount of time. And when you think you did well on an exam, think again. Be prepared for exam feedback that doesn't make any sense - you literally have no idea why she takes points off.",
